Narrator: Only killua
understood what was happening,

55
00:04:32,539 --> 00:04:34,641
and it froze him on the spot.

56
00:04:34,675 --> 00:04:40,047
Being ignorant, the shock
for the others was much greater.

57
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:43,850
Of them, there were only two.

58
00:04:46,787 --> 00:04:50,658
