60
00:04:52,092 --> 00:04:53,860
Shoot: Has he lost it?

61
00:04:53,894 --> 00:04:57,264
Killua: Your target isn’t youpi.

62
00:04:57,297 --> 00:05:00,066
No. Hold on.

63
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:01,802
( Footsteps echoing )

64
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,141
♪

65
00:05:07,174 --> 00:05:08,609
Narrator: To killua,

